dc_title_s: Carte de la Baye de Trinquemale.
dc_description_s: Scale not given. (E 81°08ʹ34ʺ--E 81°20ʹ01ʺ/N 8°40ʹ38ʺ--N 8°27ʹ09ʺ). Nautical chart showing fortifications, bays, and islands within Trincomalee Bay. Relief shown by hachures and landforms. Depths shown by soundings. Oriented with north to the lower right. Likely extracted from Abbé Prevost's L'Histoire generale des voyages. "Suppl. au Tome VIII Number 7"--Lower left margin. Includes illustrations. In French. 1 map ; 26 x 36 cm
